This is a repository that includes UNIX desktop userspace programs and configuration files that are customized to my personal taste and needs.
dwm+dmenu+st with dark solarized theme, slock for locking the screen.
----
Dependencies:
Xlib header files
[Optional] Terminus font
[Optional] Unifont font

